You are working in a React 19 + Vite 7 + TypeScript project.

Architecture:
- App entry, routes and providers live in `src/app/`
- Features live in `src/features/<name>/`
- Shared code lives in `src/shared/`
- Layout shells live in `src/layouts/`

Rules:
- Use `@/` imports for code under `src/`
- Default-export page components
- Use functional components only
- Prefer CSS Modules for component styling
- Do not import one feature from another feature directly
- Run `pnpm lint` after changes
